metadata.name: Tree Thoughts Founder Token
metadata.description:
If you ever need a peaceful place to think, consider finding a tree that can shade you and sing to you in the breeze. 

Tree Thoughts is a project by Koko of UnwantedCrypto. The goal of Tree Thoughts is to empower creators through community with an emphasis on creativity and mental health.

By minting this token you are supporting independent content creation and the goal of empowering others through educational content on web3, content creation, and many other topics.

Tree Thoughts will start rolling out throughout 2023, and as an early supporter, this Founder Token will provide you with benefits and utility within the Tree Thoughts project.

Thank you for reading this!
